-- Genentech plans to buy Tanox for about $919 mln
-- 
-- Thu Nov 9, 2006 6:03pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/11/09/us-tanox-genentech-idUSWEN959720061109

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Genentech Inc. DNA.N said on Thursday it plans to buy biotechnology company Tanox TNOX.O for about $919 million. 

 Genentech said it plans to pay $20 per share in the anticipated transaction.